item.title: Status of Indian Railway PNR on Facebook Messenger
item.description: Bhaina Bot Bhaina is a facebook messenger based chat bot that helps you with current status of any Indian Railway PNR. You don’t have to install any extra application on your mobile to use this service. Give it a try on your messenger!
